comments.body:
Magic attach-disk incantation example for EBS testing:

{noformat}
attach-disk --domain frobinator --source /dev/disk/by-path/ip-10.101.1.24:3260-iscsi-iqn.2001-04.com.example:disk1.b24.eucalyptus-systems.com-lun-1 --target vdc --driver qemu --cache none
{noformat}

for some reason, omitting the {{--driver}} option causes the {{--cache}} option to be ignored, which prevents migration.
